                          <desc type="Unclear">An unclear note, possibly referring to an owner of the book.</desc>
                          <q xml:lang="gez">አምላክ፡ ለኵሉ፡ መንፈስ፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ዘሥጋ፡ ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወንድም፡ የመጻፍ፡ ስሙ፡ ቤዝወኒ፡</q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a3">
                          <locus target="#2r"/>
