                             most probably added later, in a different hand and bigger script, disregarding the layout.</desc>
                          <q xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላከ፡ እስራኤል፡</hi></q>
                       </item>
                       
                       <item xml:id="a4">
                          <locus from="87rb" to="88vb"/>
                          <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6818ZenaLebna">A short history of the kings Lǝbna Dǝngǝl, Galāwdewos, Minās and Śarḍa Dǝngǝl.</title></desc>
                          <q xml:lang="gez">ንጽሕፍ፡ ዜናሁ፡ ለንጉሥነ፡ ኦርቶዶክሳዊ፡ ወናግ፡ ሰገድ፡ <sic resp="DN">በይሰመይ፡</sic> ወኮነ፡ 
